<TEXT>
democratic presidential nominee michael 
dukakis is trying hard to beat the rap that his experience as a 
governor has not equipped him to handle national defense and 
foreign policy 
he has talked tough on military spending and driven an m1 tank 
met with foreign leaders from soviet foreign minister eduard 
